---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Updates — Wenji Makes" description="Mod development notes and release updates from Wenji.">
  <article class="content-page">
    <h1>Updates</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:40px;">Development notes, release announcements, and behind-the-scenes work.</p>

    <div class="placeholder-box">
      <div style="font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:12px;">📝</div>
      <p style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Development journal coming soon</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;margin-top:6px;">I’ll use this space for mod progress, new feature previews, and release notes.</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:12px;">
        For released work, visit <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/profile/IamWENJI/mods?gameId=1303" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nexus Mods</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://ko-fi.com/wenjimods" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ko-fi</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
